  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-03 stale dataset)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. A model revision was issued on 2025-11-14 to update turbulence closure coefficients; the primary experimental hemolysis dataset retains a dataVintage of 2025-10-22, predating the revision. The assessment narrative asserts the turbulence-coefficient change was 'not material to hemolysis-index predictions' and does not require re-validation against the dataset, but no formal sensitivity study or re-validation exercise was performed to substantiate that claim.",
