      "description": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against in-vitro measurements at 5 flow-speed operating points. Mean absolute error 8.3%, within the pre-specified 10% acceptance band. Dataset vintage 2025-10-22; model revision issued 2025-11-14. Assessment team judged the turbulence-coefficient update immaterial to hemolysis outputs; no re-run against post-revision predictions was performed."
