      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal mapping of validation-case input parameters to COU input parameters with documented equivalency rationale and quantified mismatch tolerances.",
      "rationale": "Informal mapping of FDA pump operating conditions to VAD COU conditions documented in a memo but not formally assessed. Hematocrit and temperature offsets between validation and COU not propagated to prediction uncertainty. Epistemic gap at MRL 5."
